### You have rent arrears 

Your landlord can take steps to evict you. Paying the rent after repairs are completed wonâ€™t always protect you from eviction.

### You moved in after March 2019 

Your landlord must make sure your home is fit to live in.

### You have proof of health or safety risks 

You can report the problem to the council and their environmental health team may arrange an inspection. Environmental health can order your landlord to carry out repairs or improve conditions.
